      "content": "it feels like more than just a pause though. like you said, the system has already decided. it's not just a bad semester, it's just... everything. i look at the future and i don't see a way out, just more of this same crushing weight. it's like i'm being forced to keep running a race i've already lost. is there even a point to trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken?",
